{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "craftea-backend-2026",
		"name": "Craftea Backend",
		"description": "Collection complète pour tester les 5 micro-services Craftea : User, Artist, Catalog, Interaction, Order.\n\n**Workflow recommandé :**\n1. Register un buyer → Login → copier le token\n2. Register un admin → Login → créer catégories/tags\n3. Register un artist → Login → créer profil, shop, produits\n4. Tester favoris et avis sur les produits\n5. Créer des commandes\n\n**Images produits :** Les images sont uploadées sur MinIO (Object Storage). Les requêtes Create/Update Product utilisent `multipart/form-data` avec le champ `images` (fichiers). Les URLs publiques MinIO sont stockées en base.\n\nLes variables `{{user_url}}`, `{{artist_url}}`, `{{catalog_url}}`, `{{interaction_url}}`, `{{order_url}}` et `{{token}}` sont pré-configurées.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{ "key": "user_url", "value": "http://localhost:3001" },
		{ "key": "artist_url", "value": "http://localhost:3002" },
		{ "key": "catalog_url", "value": "http://localhost:3003" },
		{ "key": "interaction_url", "value": "http://localhost:3004" },
		{ "key": "order_url", "value": "http://localhost:3005" },
		{ "key": "token", "value": "" },
		{ "key": "refresh_token", "value": "" },
		{ "key": "user_id", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "artist_id", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "shop_id", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "product_id", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "category_id", "value": "1" },
